<div class="page" id="page-services">
  <section style="padding-top:110px">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-label">What we fix</div>
      <h2 class="section-title">Every business has operational problems. We solve them.</h2>
      <p class="section-intro">People first. Process second. Technology third. We diagnose the human system underneath the operational failure and build what works &mdash; for the people who have to use it every day.</p>

      <div style="max-width:620px;margin-bottom:2.5rem;padding:1.25rem;border-left:3px solid var(--copper);border-radius:0">
        <p style="font-size:.88rem;color:var(--charcoal);margin-bottom:.6rem"><strong style="color:var(--navy)">Design judgment:</strong> We don't build the most sophisticated system. We build the right one &mdash; configurable where it needs to be, maintainable by the team that inherits it, and designed for the person using it at 4pm on a Friday.</p>
        <p style="font-size:.88rem;color:var(--charcoal);margin-bottom:.6rem"><strong style="color:var(--navy)">Systems thinking:</strong> We don't solve for the immediate problem alone. We identify patterns and design systems that can be reused, modularized, and productized.</p>
        <p style="font-size:.88rem;color:var(--charcoal);margin-bottom:.6rem"><strong style="color:var(--navy)">Decision system design:</strong> We make organizational decision logic explicit &mdash; who owns what decisions, what inputs are required, how outcomes are measured.</p>
        <p style="font-size:.88rem;color:var(--charcoal)"><strong style="color:var(--navy)">Narrative that sells:</strong> We translate complex architecture into the user's language. Every competitive proposal we've led has made the shortlist.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="service-category">
        <h3>My operation is broken</h3>
        <p>For organizations where the work isn't flowing, teams aren't aligned, or programs are off the rails.</p>
        <div class="service-list">
          <div class="service-item">Fractional COO / VP of Operations</div>
          <div class="service-item">Operational diagnostic (2-week embedded)</div>
          <div class="service-item">Program rescue &amp; turnaround</div>
          <div class="service-item">Post-acquisition integration</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="service-category">
        <h3>I need technology leadership</h3>
