          <div class="service-item">Enterprise architecture &amp; modernization</div>
          <div class="service-item">Salesforce ecosystem strategy</div>
          <div class="service-item">System integration design (MuleSoft, APIs)</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="service-category">
        <h3>I need AI but don't know where to start</h3>
