    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-label">Accelerator Light</div>
      <h2 class="section-title">Scale your operations, keep your equity.</h2>
      <p class="section-intro">Most startups don't fail from a lack of capital; they fail from a lack of functional operating systems. We've unbundled the traditional accelerator model to offer execution, architecture, and peer-accountability without the bloated equity requirements.</p>

