        <div class="service-list">
          <div class="service-item">MVP architecture &amp; build planning</div>
          <div class="service-item">Team structure &amp; first technical hires</div>
          <div class="service-item">Scaling from founder-led to team-led</div>
          <div class="service-item">AI governance frameworks</div>
        </div>
