      <p style="margin-top:2rem;font-size:.95rem;color:var(--warm-gray)">Ready to build a system that works? <a href="javascript:void(0)" onclick="event.preventDefault();showPage('contact')" style="color:var(--copper)">Apply for the next cohort &rarr;</a></p>
